en’sBlessing,June28 383\nBe careful not to give the enemy any advantage by your unguarded\nwords. Keep looking to Jesus. He is your strength....\nBe so considerate, so tender, so compassionate, that the atmo-\nsphere surrounding you will be fragrant with Heaven’s blessing.39\n39TheYouth’sInstructor,September12,1901."
