onofSonship,October31 641\nby the world. The more we come into fellowship with Christ and\nheaven, the less will be our fellowship with the world, for we are\nnot of the world.43\n43TheReviewandHerald,February28,1888.\n642 ThatIMayKnowHim\nNovember"
