athway of those\naround us. We shall reveal the gracious character of our Redeemer,\nExampleoftheBelievers,November6 655\nand many will be drawn by our influence to “behold the Lamb of\nGod, which taketh away the sin of the world” (John 1:29).8\n8TheReviewandHerald,March6,1888."
