 You will be appreciated for all that you are worth.\n“Whatsoever thy hand findeth to do, do it with thy might” (Ecclesi-\nastes 9:10). “Not slothful in business; fervent in spirit; serving the\nLord” (Romans 12:11).28\n28TheS.D.A. BibleCommentary5:1112."
